'''雷蒙·波特'''（{{lang-en|Raymond Porter}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員、配音演員及有聲書旁白，參與領域涉及真人和動畫電影、電視和電子遊戲。他較著名的是在《[[查克·史奈德之正義聯盟|查克·史奈德之正義聯盟]]》（2021年）中飾演反派[[達克賽德|烏克薩斯／達克賽德]]。

== 職業生涯 ==
雷·波特出演過幾部{{le|李察·瑞奇|Richard Rich (filmmaker)}}的動畫作品，且偶爾出演電視劇。當他在2017年電影《[[正義聯盟_(電影)|正義聯盟]]》中飾演反派[[達克賽德|烏克薩斯／達克賽德]]後引起大眾關注，成為首位在真人電影中詮釋該角的演員<ref>{{Cite tweet |first=Ray |last=Porter |user=Ray_Porter |number=1263982099377188864|title=That said, and because I've been given permission... Hi, I'm Ray. I played Darkseid in Zack Snyder's "Justice League". There. It's out now.|date=2020-05-22 |access-date=2020-07-27}}</ref>。但達克賽德並未出現在院線剪輯版中<ref>{{cite web |last=Kit |first=Borys |title="It Will Be an Entirely New Thing": Zack Snyder's $20M-Plus 'Justice League' Cut Plans Revealed |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/justice-league-snyder-cut-plans-revealed-it-will-be-an-new-thing-1295102 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |publisher=MRC |date=2020-05-20 |access-date=2020-07-27 |archive-date=2020-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200601065043/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/justice-league-snyder-cut-plans-revealed-it-will-be-an-new-thing-1295102 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，意味著導演剪輯版《[[查克·史奈德之正義聯盟|查克·史奈德之正義聯盟]]》（2021年）才是該角在真人電影中的首次登場<ref>{{cite web |last=Beasley |first=Tom |title=Zack Snyder unveils first look at Darkseid in the Snyder Cut of 'Justice League' |url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/snyder-cut-darkseid-justice-league-085635158.html |website=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] |publisher=[[Verizon_Media|Verizon Media]] |access-date=2020-07-27 |date=2020-05-28 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614070552/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/snyder-cut-darkseid-justice-league-085635158.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。波特透過[[動作捕捉|動作捕捉]]出演達克賽德<ref>{{cite web |last=Jirak |first=Jamie |title=Ray Porter Confirms He Worked With Steppenwolf Actor Ciaran Hinds on Zack Snyder's 'Justice League' |url=https://comicbook.com/movies/news/ray-porter-confirms-darkseid-steppenwolf-ciaran-hinds-zack-snyder-justice-league/ |website=ComicBook.com |access-date=2020-07-27 |date=2020-05-24 |archive-date=2020-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602075115/https://comicbook.com/movies/news/ray-porter-confirms-darkseid-steppenwolf-ciaran-hinds-zack-snyder-justice-league/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並嘗試了各種不同的聲調來詮釋該角的聲音<ref>{{cite web |last=Chichizola |first=Corey |title=The Snyder Cut's Darkseid Actor Reveals How He Played The Iconic Villain In 'Justice League' |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2547453/the-snyder-cuts-darkseid-actor-reveals-how-he-played-the-iconic-villain-in-justice-league |website=CinemaBlend |access-date=2020-07-27 |date=2020-06-03 |archive-date=2020-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603215652/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2547453/the-snyder-cuts-darkseid-actor-reveals-how-he-played-the-iconic-villain-in-justice-league |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

